high_descs: Go left and then left again to stand in front of the green trash can in the corner.
Pick the newspaper up out of the trash can.
Turn around and go right and then left to cross the room and turn to face the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a newspaper and turn a lamp on.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the door, then turn to your left again and go to the green garbage can, on the floor, in the right corner of the room.
Pull out the newspaper from the green garbage can.
Turn to your left and walk across the room, then turn to your left again and walk across the room to the lamp in the right corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp in the right corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the living room lamp.

high_descs: Turn left, then left around the table again and head towards the green trash can to your right.
Take out the newspaper from the green trash can in front of you.
Turn around, then right, then left again around the table and face the brown lamp in the corner to your right.
Turn the lamp on in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Get ready to read the newspaper on the couch.
